ight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">请尽快联系客服人员进行修改。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">26、真实姓名填写错误如何修改？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">一经绑定，用户本人无法直接修改真实姓名，但可以联系客服人员进行修改。操作流程如下：</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 联系客服人员（可通过电话、QQ、邮件等途径），说明修改的原因；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 客服部收到授权后，由专员核实信息提交报告，交领导批准签字；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 主管领导签字后，技术专员在有人监督的情况下，修改用户的错误信息。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">27、验证码有何作用？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">设置验证码是为了提高系统的安全性，它可以有效防止针对某个特定账号的暴力破解（即用特定程序进行不断的登录尝试），使用验证码也是目前各网站通行的安全措施。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">28、登录时为什么看不到验证码或总是提示验证码不正确？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">看不到验证码或者总是提示验证码输入错误，可能的原因有：</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 网速过慢，请多刷新几次页面。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 输入错误，数字有全角和半角之分，请换用半角方式输入。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 安全级别设置过高，请将IE的安全级别设为“默认级别”。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 网页没有自动更新，请先设置浏览器的“Internet临时文件”为“自动”更新。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">29、忘记了登录密码怎么办？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 请及时提供相应信息给客服。系统将重置一个新密码，并把新密码发送到用户注册时提交的电子邮箱中，为保障账户安全，建议用户登录后立即修改密码。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">30、如何查询购买彩票的记录？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">在"用户中心"左侧选择"交易记录"，即可查看购买彩票的记录。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">31、索回密码却收取不到邮件怎么办？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">可以联系客服人员。操作流程如下：</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 确定您注册时输入的邮箱地址是您现在使用的邮箱。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 耐心等待，有时候网络会延时。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 请查看一下您的垃圾邮件中，是否有取回密码的邮件。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 邮箱自身的问题，存在收不到邮件的情况。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 您的邮箱拒收或网络等原因造成邮件接收失败。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">32、如何修改登录密码？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">操作流程如下：</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 登录后进入首页，点击右侧的“用户中心”。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 在“用户中心”页面左侧“账号信息”中选择“修改密码”。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 用户输入旧密码，并设置新密码。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 提交信息，修改密码成功，系统提示成功信息。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">33、用户为保证账户资金安全应注意哪些事项？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">彩民用户必须注意自己电脑中是否有键盘记录或远程控制等木马程序，使用病毒实时监控程序和网络防火墙并注意升级更新操作系统厂商所提供的安全补丁；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 尽量不要在公共场所（如网吧）等登录本网站；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 尽量在不同场合使用有所区别的密码；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 牢记密码，如作记录则应妥善保管；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 密码不得告 诉他人，包括自己的亲朋好友；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 在登录或网上支付密码输入时，应防止左右可疑的人窥视；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 预留密码时不要选用您的身份证、生日、电话、门牌、街巷、重复或连续等易被他人破译的数字。建议选用既不易被他人猜到，又方便记忆的密码；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 发现泄密的危险时，及时更换密码；不定期更换密码。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">34、为什么登录后长时间不登录，要重新登录？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">用户登录后，长时间不操作电脑，系统就认为用户离开自己的电脑了。为了避免别人趁机使用您的账户投注和保护彩民用户账户的安全，系统有要求用户重新登录的设置。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">35、为什么用户不能更改注册时提交的用户名？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">用户进行投注时，用户名是保障自身利益的唯一凭证。一经注册，不允许更改。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">36、怎么保护中奖者的个人