l,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 没有升级IE浏览器，导致加密级别过低，无法进入银行系统。 请升级到8.0及以上版本。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 上网环境或上网方式受限，可能是网络服务商限制，如有条件更换一种上网方式或环境。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 瞬间网络不通，尝试刷新页面；如果刷新不能解决问题，可能由于浏览器设置缓存，请在IE菜单—工具—Internet选项—点击"删除cookies"和"删除文件"，用以清除临时文件。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">40、没有接到银联打过来的电话怎么办？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">在线支付是即时向银行系统提交支付信息的，所以如果出现银行卡卡内金额不足、意外断线等状况而导致支付的不成功，请重新提交一次充值并按在线支付的方法操作。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">41、提款金额有没有限制？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">本站单笔提款最低金额为100元，无最高限制。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">42、提款次数有没有限制？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">本公司不限制提款次数。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">43、提款需要手续费吗？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 达到提款条件才能取款。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 提款不限次数，手续费根据本站设定。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 提款时所产生的银行手续费将全部由本站为您承担。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">44、提款不成功怎么办？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">提款不成功分两种情况：</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 提款申请未成功：</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">1、提款金额大于账户实有金额。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">2、提款时填写的提款密码与用账户信息设置的提款密码不一致。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">3、银行卡信息不符合规定格式。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 申请提款成功，但款项没有到达指定账户：</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">1、银行卡卡号填写错误，与用户姓名不符，银行退单。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">一旦发生上述现象，请及时联系客服，由客服人员为您服务。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">45、如何查询提款记录？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 用户登录后点击首页右侧的"提款"。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 在提款页面，点击右上角"查看提款记录"。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">规则说明</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">46、我从来没买过彩票，这些彩种都怎么玩？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">点击首页的“玩法”后进入玩法规则页面，选择想要投注的彩种并查看其详细玩法。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">47、什么是标准投注？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">标准投注包括单式投注和复式投注。</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">48、什么是单式投注？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">单式投注即用户选择一注号码进行投注。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">49、什么是复式投注？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">复式投注即用户将两注以上号码的组合方式作为一组投注号码同时投注。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">50、什么是机选投注？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">机选指由系统随机产生投注号码进行投注。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">51、什么是直选投注？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">直选指将所选号码以唯一的排列方式进行投注。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">52、什么是组选投注？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">组选指将所选号码的所有排列方式作为一注号码进行投注。如一注3D组选号码的 3个数字有两个数字相同，则有3种不同的排列方式，因而就有3个中奖机会，这种组选投注方式简称组选3。如一注3D组选号码的3个数字各不相同，则有6种 不同的排列方式，因而就有6个中奖机会，这种组选投注方式简称组选6。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">53、什么是追号投注？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">追号指将一注或一组号码进行两期或两期以上的投注。追号可分为连续追号和间隔追号，连续追号指追号的期数是连续的，间隔追号指追号的期数不连续。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">54、什么是和值投注？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">和值指投注各号码相加之和，如3D号码123，其和值为6。和值投注即用该和值的所有号码进行投注，如用户选择3D直选和值1，共3注：001、010和100。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">55、什么是包号投注？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">包号投注指将用户所选择号码的所有组合形式进行投注。如3D组三包号01，共2注：001和110。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">56、什么是胆拖投注？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">胆拖投注也叫基数组合投注，通常由胆码和拖码组成。胆码是用户认为出现机会非常大的号码，在所投注的每一注彩票里都固定出现；拖码即彩民补充的其他不同的号码。拖码与胆码共同组成一注完整的投注号码。</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">57、为什么号码导入不成功？</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">号码导入，有两点要求：号码导入时，必须是文本格式（.txt）</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">文本内容有格式要求(双色球、3D)：</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">a、 确认要导入的号码文件位置,如果没有请新建(英文状态下书写)；</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">b、 文本格式按照相关彩种单式手动输入号码的规则；</span><br><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">58、如何查询追号记录？</span><br><span open="" sans",="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 14px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="" style="font-family: ">· 用户登录本站，进入会员中心，点击左侧“交易记录”。 · 选择下拉“全部投注”。 · 选择“追号记录”查看，即可查看追号记录。</span><br></p>

